title: PES PERFECT - GFX MOD Suite
description:
What's PES PERFECT - GFX MOD Suite?
PES PERFECT is a graphics mod for Pro Evolution Soccer 2017.

It does not contain the game. It's just an addition for the game.

It's a combination of all-new pitches/turfs, new lighting for some stadiums and, of course... ReShade.
It's not recommended to use one without the other. Since I worked on the new pitches from scratch at the same time I was creating the ReShade preset, which means without it, it will probably will look bad.​

Thanks
